#: src/1925-optional-match-vert.md:191
msgid "Detailed design"
msgstr "詳細設計"

#: src/1925-optional-match-vert.md:194
msgid ""
"I don't know about the implementation but the grammar could be updated so "
"that an optional `|` is allowed at the beginning. Nothing else in the "
"grammar should need updating."
msgstr ""

#: src/1925-optional-match-vert.md:198
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"// Before\n"
"match_pat : pat [ '|' pat ] * [ \"if\" expr ] ? ;\n"
"// After\n"
"match_pat : '|' ? pat [ '|' pat ] * [ \"if\" expr ] ? ;\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

